      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "In our previous report, it was elucidated that deposition rate can be used to control orientations and stresses of YSZ lms independently.  Low deposition rates (<5 nm min À1 ) during the initial nucleation stages result in (111) oriented lms while higher rates (>15 nm min À1 ) yield (100) oriented lms.",
